    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻击</span></p><p>造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素伤害</span>。</p><p>如果此技能为<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">重击</span>，则使敌方出战角色附属<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">引雷</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/15/88072335/ead1e5139681f49400a80a2ebb10fb2a_9142268802200794798.png",
                "id": "talent6384",
                "key": "指尖雷暴",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "指尖雷暴"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素战技</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素伤害</span>，如果敌方角色未附属<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">引雷</span>，则使其附属<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">引雷</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/15/88072335/af99fb6b223af8aab53e4447b06483ba_7084265145704695915.png",
                "id": "talent91315",
                "key": "苍雷",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "苍雷"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素伤害</span>，召唤<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">蔷薇雷光</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/15/88072335/e225f8fa5e9a435290d33b7b93b4e376_8776035726629748844.png",
                "id": "talent17099",
                "key": "蔷薇的雷光",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "蔷薇的雷光"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">召唤物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">结束阶段：</span>造成2点<span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">雷元素伤害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次数：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/15/88072335/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_1936479146483566311.png",
                "id": "talent12336",
                "key": "蔷薇雷光",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/15/88072335/2b3f9718f47e31a775816000450f000e_4026036933284988187.png",
                "title": "蔷薇雷光"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附着雷元素，可发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超载</span>：本伤害+2，目标强制切换到下一个角色</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超导</span>：本伤害+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">感电</span>：本伤害+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">原激化</span>：本伤害+1，生成使下2次草元素或雷元素伤害+1的[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">激化领域</span>]</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/15/88072335/11ea6117480145a30b7893f1e8bd7115_3632427383009674435.png",
                "id": "talent483",
                "key": "雷元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "雷元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">重击</span></strong></p><p>我方开始行动前，如果元素骰总数为偶数，则进行的「普通攻击」将被视为「重击」。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">引雷</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">状态</span></p><p>此状态初始具有2层「引雷」；重复附属时，叠加1层「引雷」。「引雷」最多可以叠加到4层。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">结束阶段：</span>叠加1层「引雷」。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">所附属角色受到苍雷伤害时：</span>移除此状态，每层「引雷」使此伤害+1。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/15/88072335/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_6952381223569210362.png",
                "id": "talent48276",
                "key": "规则术语",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "规则术语"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
